---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | IntelliFill" description="IntelliFill Terms of Service - Rules and guidelines for using our service.">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-slate-900 px-4 py-6 border-b border-slate-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Content -->
  <main class="bg-slate-900 px-4 py-16">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-4xl prose prose-invert prose-slate">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mt-2">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <section class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          By accessing or using IntelliFill, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use our service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          IntelliFill provides AI-powered document processing and form automation services. We use optical character recognition (OCR) and machine learning to extract data from documents and assist with form filling.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          You are responsible for:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials</li>
          <li>All activities that occur under your account</li>
          <li>Notifying us immediately of any unauthorized access</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">4. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          You agree not to:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Upload illegal, fraudulent, or harmful content</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
          <li>Use the service for any unlawful purpose</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the service</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">5. Subscriptions and Payments</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          PRO subscriptions are billed monthly. You can cancel at any time from your account settings. Refunds are provided in accordance with our refund policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          You retain ownership of documents you upload. IntelliFill retains ownership of the service, software, and associated intellectual property.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          IntelliFill is provided "as is" without warranties. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">9. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mt-4">
          For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@intellifill.com" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">legal@intellifill.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
